  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe- \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u00a0\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 -\u00a0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Podujana Peramuna should not support Kota-Ranil conspiracies - Frontline Socialist Party",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government led by Gotabaya Rajapaksa has lost the Lok Sabha. The power vested in the people has been exhausted.",
        "If the Budujana Peramuna party self-evaluates and comes forward to correct itself, it should not support quota-run conspiracies.",
        "Kumar Gunaratnam, General Secretary of the Front Socialist Party, commented in this regard,",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa's Mandate of the People obtained in November 2019 has been revoked. The two-thirds majority power available to Budujana Peramuna has also been exhausted.",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Ranil Wickramasinghe's conspiracies cannot be helped if there are people who come to Budujana Peramuna to self-evaluate and correct themselves.",
        "You are the ones who are responsible for the economic damage and political crisis in the country in the last two and a half years. Self-evaluation should come before creating a harmonious environment that does not hinder the struggle.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe and Gotabaya Rajapaksa or Bashil Rajapaksa should not get involved in their conspiracies.",
        "We will unite in Parliament and everywhere to defeat Gotabaya Rajapaksa conspiracies, including Ranil Wickramasinghe, who are trying to create a dictatorial trend in the country by hiding within the ranks of political institutions.",
        "The country was not pushed into crisis by the protest or by the protestors. The main reason for the crisis was the decisions of the Gotabaya Rajapaksa government.",
        "A new all-party government should be built in the country to demonstrate a credible and stable government to the people of the country and to the international community.",
        "Considering the crisis situation of the country, other parties including the main opposition party representing the parliament should work together with other parties of the country to make the people's uprising a success.",
        "He also said that the people involved in the uprising should take into consideration the demands made by them and jointly come forward to fulfill them."
      ],
